{"tid":720622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又黎多次] 台網紅谷阿莫疑侵權用世界盃影片","createTime":"2018-06-28T05:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T08:18:15.000Z","uid":77196,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"51670f2adbd74f743917de49545d921bdff08434","tid":720622,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"台灣網絡紅人谷阿莫日前以本屆世界盃賽事影片剪輯約4分鐘影片，被取得台灣轉播權的愛爾達電視發函警告，同時通報國際足協(FIFA)。<br />\n<br />\n谷阿莫日前使用本屆世界盃賽事影片，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>剪輯約4分鐘的「谷阿莫4分鐘教你假裝有在發落2018世足賽(1-8天賽事)」</strong></span>。雖然他事後刪了影片，但恐已涉及侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾達電視表示，谷阿莫未經授權使用世界盃影片，恐涉及侵權，上周已發函告知需取得授權才能使用，目前仍未確定和解或提出控告，而谷阿莫則未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n谷阿莫以在YouTube及Facebook上傳「X分鐘看完一部XX的電影」爆紅，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>早前有5家片商認為他評述的電影短片屬侵權，並提出起訴</strong></span>。"},{"pid":"8663198d2df1f44f3371a3a1088f351dddaeea4a","tid":720622,"uid":23468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"依家youtube愈來愈多呢d channel，d view仲要個個百幾萬一條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbeeffbaa9bab9eb4d3ef0f40b86942ae5a16a40","tid":720622,"uid":21423,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb7c2ffea5b8aeebec46d43fec96c4a5a56402d4","tid":720622,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8663198d2df1f44f3371a3a1088f351dddaeea4a","tid":720622,"uid":23468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"依家youtube愈來愈多呢d channel，d view仲要個個百幾萬一條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl